      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZAP DEVERE (6) is a strong stayer well performed over the longer races. Was a strong winner last time (34.78) over 600m at this track in a Grade 5. Form at the trip excellent including two wins. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Sure to prove hard to beat. BRUTE FORCE (8) goes very well here starting eight times for three wins and three minors. In the money last time at Sandown (29.61) in a Grade 5, finishing a half a length second. Looks one of the chances. RALPH WIGGUM (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (30.36) in a Special conditions H at Sandown. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. LAMIA TAYA (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
